name: East Earth: Rootin' Tootin' Robots
description: Are you human enough to navigate through East Earth? The Robot hosts have taken over the park and have been corrupted. We need you to enter the park and find out what object is making the hosts go haywire. We're not certain what device is corrupting the assets but we need to find it, quickly. Assume all hosts are aggressive. Neutralize any assets that interfere with finding that object!
